# Scratch ESP-IDF projects under tools/ that were scaffolded from upstream
# IDF examples — see CLAUDE.md for how to regenerate them when slave fw
# needs a rebuild. Listed individually because git can't re-include a path
# whose parent has been ignored.
tools/c6_slave_fw/
tools/c6_ota_flasher/
# tools/bt_agent IS our own code — committed below — but its build output
# and generated sdkconfig are still scratch.
tools/bt_agent/build/
tools/bt_agent/sdkconfig
tools/bt_agent/sdkconfig.old

# research/_sources/ are clones of upstream reference repos
# (aasdk, openauto, headunit, waveshare_p4_4_3, WirelessAndroidAutoDongle).
# Not committed — see CLAUDE.md for the URLs.
research/_sources/

# Local bench WiFi creds — present only on dev machines.
# When the file exists, wifi_manager forces STA mode and joins this network
# instead of running its own SoftAP. Also catches the `.disabled` rename we
# use to temporarily flip back to AP mode without losing the creds.
main/bench_wifi.h*
logs/
